metadata.name: AWAC #1
metadata.description: We are Apes With Attitude Club a collection of 2,222 skeleton Apes living on the Eth blockchain. The plan is to build together as a project driven community to reach our goals and succeed as one family.This is our first step in our long journey together as one! taking you from the physical world to the virtual world then back to the physical optimising web3 to its maximum . The strategy behind our Roadmap is to make a genuine impact in the NFT space and real world giving back to the community and people who have believed and supported us
